Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:35.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:40.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:47.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:52.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:57.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:00.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:03.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:06.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:11.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:14.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:19.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:23.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:26.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:28.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:31.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:38.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:35.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜欢着紧张的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:40.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}兴奋起来走向更广阔的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:47.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:52.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只专注于眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:57.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}谁都无法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:01:00.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前进的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:03.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}连同那份泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:06.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部开始闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:11.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此将宿于手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:14.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}尽情挥扬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果断地  径直地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:19.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向着明天全力进发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:23.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在转瞬即逝之间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:26.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}实现那梦中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:28.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}无论它多么虚幻和遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:31.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和仅属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:38.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹剑节奏响彻永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:51.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第24话\N剑与道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么想要退部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说点什么嘛  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮不上大家的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为小珠你的加入  剑道部才越来越好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次也还是输掉比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输掉比赛不光是小珠的错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是因为我不得不胜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不得不胜  所以不可以输
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那场大赛上我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我强的人有很多很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮不上大家的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道还有什么继续剑道的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这样说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你再也不参加活动也好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没交给老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学也没有来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去教室的时候已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先开始练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫老师过来  你们就先去练摆振吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君  宫崎同学说了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我派不上用场吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！从勇次君开始连续30次  喊出声来！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  也不能强拉她回头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  部团活动参加与否还是要遵从个人意识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  今天我有点事情  不能去道场了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山他们的事情明天做个决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要逃避问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是顾问吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  辛苦～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…老师他都说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个顾问脑子在想什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是剑道部最大危机呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  总会有办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要考虑考虑那些一年级的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是顾问吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的剑道  结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整天都不碰竹剑  有几年没这么做了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子火焰剑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这样就结束了  Blade Braver！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管几次我都会复活的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不管几次我都保护给你看！人们的笑容！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…前辈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天向学校请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生病了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想倒也不会是那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会一起去探病吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也不在家里  手机也不接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是不是让她静静比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃那边我回去时再过去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…纪梨乃前辈最近是不是有点怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没那回事哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  别在意小事  来练习来练习啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师今天也不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好冷清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过原来就不算热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:14.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（无他）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆胎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本不用陪我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  你不再练剑道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也说用不着刻意去练
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都是刻意在练吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你有没有想过想要让自己的剑道变得更强？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有想过想赢过那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠以前问过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输掉的时候是什么样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那一定就是小珠现在感受到的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  小珠你输给她  输给凛所以很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你以前一直都比别人强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在面对这份不甘心不知道如何是好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输掉…原来是这样子的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用不着放弃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道早已把今后的道路准备完全了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那份不甘心为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力并最终取得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与不甘心比起来还有远胜于它的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力并取胜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小珠不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为输了很多次所以明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白这点之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会喜欢上剑道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动起来动起来  安藤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  突然找我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  有件事情请您务必告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.27,0:10:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您教我与上段对战的方法吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要打赢她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  看来终于开窍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊  你们那边不就有个打上段的么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了  老师用上段打赢过石桥老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您了  请教我和上段对战的方法吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被逼急了乱打上去的一剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不会打什么上段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您了  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有什么可教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来就强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常练剑道的话  总有一日会输
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会出现一定打不赢的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系  部团活动这种东西只要高兴就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴就好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想忘记今天察觉的这份不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于开始了…自己的剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要面对自己的失败！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来！石田！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道不好好面对就谈不上开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:12:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去道场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从城里骑自行车一直过来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是明天再开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  大家都在担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  别跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和段君之间发生什么事情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是凯莉的事情的话不早就过去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是二刀流  只要努力练习超过她不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎和你怎么会明白我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要对方跟我一样努力练习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她的差距就永远不会缩小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有可能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一味地陷在对方的话里面这怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是凯莉她元旦啊盂盆节啊圣诞节也会休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差距绝对可以缩小的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上她要花多少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果努力也都是白费的话  练剑道还有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要胡说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能说努力都是白费  谁敢这么说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没有这样想过！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是输了两次就想放弃  想消沉  想逃避的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没资格这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想放弃的话就给我赢了再放弃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别糟蹋了我的特训！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你不想活了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我做好准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从头开始锻炼直到我打倒你为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了  你突然跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是你请假不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小鞘…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想什么？连你都想退出吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想这样校长就能网开一面…责任让部长来承担…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在能做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么总是这样笨呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难过也好痛苦也好总是笑眯眯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把一切都揽到自己头上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这样烦恼就能解决了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭有什么关系！难过有什么关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我不就可以来帮你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人烦心什么都做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果齐心协力能解决问题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来找我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自决定啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的想这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…也会跟着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就能下决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧啦  今天会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我有鼓励小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但实际上我是不是根本不理解她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有什么非赢不可的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我还是只能嘴上说说加油吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事…段君你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  只有男生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛你们  还不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休部？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？下次再来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦  等等再说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来打发下时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后大闹一场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我打  一年级的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你退后  勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不讨厌剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不相信  他也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  一年级！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹——！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  不适合我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道到最后都这么无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个交给纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日期是春天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们和部团就没什么关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也不能强行休部了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是骗人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上就是在那之后写的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠那个笨蛋的人情算是还清了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是部长做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直放在更衣室里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:19:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:20:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢指导
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样多少能理解一点小都都的感受了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问问她如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样前辈们也比较高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳  我们部什么时候开始这么热闹了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  作为部长我不想让大家太担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  虽说是部长但也是部员嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就是他们两个
